Fri November 2, 2012 - Friday Frolic w/Linda -- Wayne to Chadds Ford. Level=
 C+/B-, 13-15 mph, 50 miles. Meet at Church of the Saviour, Wayne, PA. The =
ride leaves at 9:30 am. Challenging but scenic loop from Wayne, through wes=
tern Delaware County and eastern Chester County, mostly on green & pretty c=
ountry roads. Rest stops at WAWAs at mile points 17 and 38. Rolling to hill=
y terrain, with some flat stretches here & there on Creek Rd. Total elevati=
on gain is 4600 ft. We will stop to regroup as needed. We'll pass a few hor=
se farms and country clubs, too. If you are not familiar with the Church of=
 the Saviour ride start location, we cyclists meet in the rear parking lot,=
 near the athletic field. Please note: Now that it's November with cooler t=
emperatures, starting times for the Friday Frolic will be no earlier than 9=
:30, and distances will be adjusted for the cooler weather. Cue sheets will=
 be available. The on-line route map is
 http://ridewithgps.com/routes/1846480 It is optional, but you may preregis=
ter until Thursday, November 1, 2012 at 11:59 pm.

